Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啦 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是你不對在先
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你讓我躲開
